  "text": "According to Kothyari et al. [CITATION_1] , the drag coefficient of one cylinder in a cylinder array is a function of the area concentration of cylinders aD and of the cylinder Reynolds number Re D ¼ U Q D=m. Using the empirical formula of Kothyari et al. [CITATION_2] and comparing with the C D -value recommended by Nepf [CITATION_3] , we take C D ¼ 1:2 in the present case. Using the Manning roughness coefficient n determined in Sect. 3.1 for the bed roughness, the bed shear stress is:",
